知道吗 我总是和我孩子说
You know, I tell my kids all the time

39
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:23,850
不能躺着吃口香糖 会噎住的
that they can't chew gum laying down or else they'll choke.

40
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:28,920
