How about I put this around you, OK?

49
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:18,300
很高兴认识你 奥利维亚
Nice to meet you, Olivia.

50
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:23,100
查理爸爸一号 学校登记录上记载
Papa Charlie-1, school records list

51
