我搭档现在在你家
My partner is in your house.

56
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:58,090
有什么他需要知道的吗
Is there anything he needs to know?

57
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:16,910
艾登
Aidan.

58
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,180
艾登
Aidan.

59
