until they finally came upon the home of their benevolent ruler.

148
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:38,910
他们慢慢走近房子
And they slowly walked up to the house

149
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:42,550
在敲门之前 他们脱掉雪地鞋 
and took off their snowshoes, leaned 'em up against the wall

150
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:45,550
并将它们靠墙根摆放好
before knocking on the door.

151
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:49,490
她怎么样了
How's she doing?

152
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:52,620
她时不时会用眼神与我交流 但就是不肯讲话
She's making eye contact once in a while, but she's still not talking.

153
00:10:52,690 --> 00:10:54,760
嘿 艾思梅在哪儿 为什么她没有来
Look, where's Esme? Why isn't she here?

154
00:10:54,830 --> 00:10:57,560
据我所知 她正在警局接受调查
As far as I know, she's at headquarters talking to our investigators.

155
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,430
我不想离开奥利维亚
Look, I don't want to leave Olivia,

156
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:05,000
但是我有...有个工程计划图
but I have this... this work project

157
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:08,110
原本应该... 一小时前完成的
that was due... about an hour ago.

158
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:10,950
嘿 如果你想离开 没关系的 
Hey, if you need to duck out, it's no trouble at all.

159
00:11:10,950 --> 00:11:12,110
我会陪着她
I'll stay with her.

160
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:18,780
那好吧
OK.

161
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:20,980
嘿 宝贝儿
Hey, baby.

162
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:24,090
我会很快回来 好吗
I'm gonna be back soon, OK?

163
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:27,890
有事马上通知我
Call me the minute anything changes.

164
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,490
谢了
Thanks.

165
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:36,200
艾思梅 你想到有谁可能会杀害
Esme, can you think of anyone who would want to kill

166
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,820
你的丈夫吗
your husband?

