Mostly they're aimed at my husband... or Olivia.

171
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:51,110
如今他们动手了 他们威胁到了你的家人
That's how they do it nowadays; They threaten your family.

172
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:53,980
我们外出度假的时候 保安也会放假
We go on vacation, security guards go on vacation too.

173
00:11:54,050 --> 00:11:56,050
这么说 你是刚从刚果回来
So, you just got back from the Congo?

174
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:59,220
