I came to terms a long time ago with the guilt

180
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,660
作为职业母亲与之俱来的那种愧疚that goes hand in hand with being a working mother.

181
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,670
你是何时从刚果回来的
When did you get back from the Congo?

182
00:12:12,730 --> 00:12:15,440
我不知道...
I don't know...

183
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:18,400
你早上遇到我的 九点钟的样子
You saw me this morning, what, 9am?

184
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:21,570
