187
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:30,320
你的旅行记录表明你是昨天早上到达的
your travel records state you arrived yesterday morning.

188
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:34,020
好吧 等等
OK, hang on a sec.

189
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:36,490
我没有...
I did not...

190
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:41,160
我整晚都在国宾酒店里
I was at the Ambassador Hotel all night.

191
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:43,860
2116房间 你可以去问门卫
Room 1126. You can ask the concierge.

192
00:12:43,930 --> 00:12:46,960
好吧 如此来说 你在三周都没见到
OK, so, you fly home after not seeing your daughter

193
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:49,330
丈夫和女儿的情况下飞回家 却...
and your husband for three weeks, but...

194
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,470
没有马上去见他们
you don't go see them right away?

195
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:55,570
是的 我的工作很不易 打交道的都是一些战犯
Yes. My work is difficult. I deal with war criminals,

196
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:57,310
独裁者和受迫害者
dictators, torture victims.

197
00:12:57,380 --> 00:13:00,310
我早已下定决心
I decided a long time ago

198
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:03,310
我绝不将工作带回家
that I was not going to bring that home to my family,

199
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:05,310
所以我在国宾酒店待了一晚
so I take a night at the Ambassador

200
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:08,750
梳理了一下头绪
to clear my head.

201
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:11,420
你是在指控我谋杀亲夫吗
Are you charging me with my husband's murder?

202
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:16,430
那么我想见见自己的女儿 就现在
Then I want to see my daughter. Now.

203
00:13:16,490 --> 00:13:18,760
我看看能不能帮上忙
I'll see what I can do.

204
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:24,270
她在撒谎
She's lying.

