where she doesn't call me "Uncle Elliott",

295
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:50,560
- 而是叫我"不代家叔叔" - "不代家"?
- she calls me "Uncle LPS". - LPS?

296
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:53,430
就是"不称职代理家长"
Yeah, "Lame Parental Substitute".

297
00:18:53,490 --> 00:18:56,530
消灭所有巧克力碎片饼干的总是我
You see, I'm the guy that burns all the chocolate chip cookies,

298
00:18:56,600 --> 00:19:00,800
给她读床前故事的时候 我反而先睡着
and I end up falling asleep while I'm reading her the bedtime stories.

299
00:19:00,870 --> 00:19:04,140
艾思梅 待她真的很不错
Esme, uh, Esme's really great with her,

300
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:06,870
但是 她总是不在家
but, you know, she's gone all the time.

301
00:19:06,940 --> 00:19:10,380
我们还是很为她骄傲的 因为她在外面
We're really proud of her for that, because she's out there,

302
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:13,750
努力让世界变得更完美
you know, making the world a nicer place to live.

303
00:19:13,810 --> 00:19:16,220
不过 我就不班门弄斧了
But look who I'm talking to, right?

304
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:19,080
什么意思
Um, what do you mean?

305
00:19:19,150 --> 00:19:22,390
你说你是警察局的精神病专家对吗
You said you're a psychiatrist with the police department,

306
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:24,790
那一定很忙吧
right? That's gotta be really demanding...

307
00:19:24,860 --> 00:19:29,190
在需要的时候和人沟通 帮助他们度过难关
talking to people when they really need you, helping them through tragedy.

308
00:19:29,260 --> 00:19:33,130
我...我怎么能和你妹妹
I'm... I'm nowhere near the league

309
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:35,530
相提并论呢
your sister's in.

310
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:38,900
艾登 我们刚刚抓到了艾尼沃克・阿德伊米
Aidan, we just picked up Enioke Adeyemi.

311
00:19:38,970 --> 00:19:41,540
那个父母被艾思梅辩护的童子兵杀害的家伙吗
The guy's parents who were killed by the child soldiers she's defending?

312
00:19:41,610 --> 00:19:44,210
- 对 就是他 - 另外两个呢
