313
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:47,510
其中一个已经逃出国 另外一个死了
Well, it turns out one of them's out of the country, and the other one's dead.

314
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,850
法医从华莱士家的滑门玻璃上
Forensics just lifted Adeyemi's prints

315
00:19:49,910 --> 00:19:51,780
提取到了阿德伊米的指纹
off the sliding glass doors at the Wallace house.

316
00:19:51,850 --> 00:19:54,820
在B审讯室
Interrogation Room B.

317
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:57,950
- 嗨 里奥 你要去哪儿 - 我要跟她走
- Hey, Leo, where are you going? - I'm going with her.

318
00:19:58,020 --> 00:20:01,060
- 你要甩掉我吗 - 给我打电话吧
- Oh, you're dumping me? - Call me sometime.

319
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:09,060
我在孤儿院长大 然后来到这里
I was raised in an orphanage, and then I come here,

320
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:11,600
然后有了工作 有了朋友
and I am working, and I have friends,

321
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:13,600
