and then I read the newspaper.

322
00:20:13,670 --> 00:20:17,810
法西纳・戈翁 难民 改造后的
Fasina Gowon. Refugee, reformed

323
00:20:17,870 --> 00:20:20,480
童子军 一个自由的人
child soldier, a free man.

324
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:24,210
但他杀了我的家人
But he killed my family,

325
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:26,280
